SHAPEFILE_1_COORDINATE_SYSTEM_GRANULARITY FEATURE_TYPE
DEFAULT_MACRO SHAPEFILE_OUT_WRITER_PARAMS_SHAPEFILE_1 
GUI OPTIONAL DISCLOSUREGROUP SHAPEFILE_OUT_WRITER_PARAMS_SHAPEFILE_1 SHAPEFILE_OUT_ENCODING_SHAPEFILE_1%SHAPEFILE_OUT_SPATIAL_INDEXES_SHAPEFILE_1%SHAPEFILE_OUT_COMPRESSED_FILE_SHAPEFILE_1%SHAPEFILE_OUT_DIMENSION%SHAPEFILE_OUT_DATETIME_STORAGE_SHAPEFILE_1 Writer Parameters
# ============================================================================
# The following keyword allows the user to choose what encoding to
# use for outputting the shapefile
DEFAULT_MACRO SHAPEFILE_OUT_ENCODING_SHAPEFILE_1 utf-8
SHAPEFILE_1_ENCODING "$(SHAPEFILE_OUT_ENCODING_SHAPEFILE_1)"
GUI STRING_OR_ENCODING SHAPEFILE_OUT_ENCODING_SHAPEFILE_1 fme-system%* Character Encoding
# ============================================================================
# Specifies whether or not the reader will generate spatial index files
